1)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://whc.unesco.org/en/tentativelists/548/ |title=L'ensemble monumental de Tirgu Jiu |work=UNESCO |language=French}}</ref> # Historic Centre of [[Sibiu]] and its Ensemble of Squares (2004)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://whc.unesco.org/en/tentativelists/1929/ |title=The Historic Centre of Sibiu and its Ensemble of Squares |work=UNESCO}}</ref> # Old Villages of [[Hollókő]] and [[Rimetea]] and their Surroundings (2012)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://whc.unesco.org/en/tentativelists/5683/ |title=The old villages of Hollókő and Rimetea and their surroundings |work=UNESCO}}</ref> # [[Rosia Montana Mining Cultural Landscape]] (2016)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://whc.unesco.org/en/tentativelists/6082/ |title=Roșia Montană Mining Cultural Landscape |work=UNESCO}}</ref>
